<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/paginationjs/2.0.8/pagination.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jqueryui/1.12.1/jquery-ui.min.css">  <!--使用 jQuery 的 Tooltip-->

<h2 class="text-center title">分發志願選填</h2>

<hr>

<div class="row" id="form-placementSelect">
	<div class="col-12">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-12">
				<div class="card">
					<div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">注意事項</div>
					<ol>
						<li>
							請依欲就讀校系意願由高至低依序選填最多<strong class="text-danger"> 40 </strong>個志願。
						</li>
						<li>
							填寫志願的數目及順序，與能否分發之關係甚大，建議善用<strong class="text-danger"> 40 </strong>個志願之機會，切勿集中填寫某些學校科系之志願，更不宜僅填 1、2 個志願。
						</li>
					</ol>
					<div class="card-body">
						<p>
							<strong>操作說明</strong>
							<ol>
								<li>
									請於左欄招生校系清單，點選 <span class="badge badge-info"><i class="fa fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></span> 將志願加入右欄。
								</li>
								<li>
									於右欄已填選志願可以點選 <span class="badge badge-danger"><i class="fa fa-times" aria-hidden="true"></i></span> 刪除志願；點選 <span class="badge badge-white"><i class="fa fa-chevron-up" aria-hidden="true"></i></span> <span class="badge badge-white"><i class="fa fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></span> 或直接輸入志願序調整志願順序。
								</li>
								<li>
									最多可選填 <strong class="text-danger">40</strong> 個志願。
								</li>
							</ol>
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<hr>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-xl-6">
				<div class="card card-bottom">
					<div class="card-header">招生校系清單</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-5">
								<select class="custom-select mb-2 mr-sm-2 mb-sm-0" id="select-optionFilter">
									<option value="cardCode">志願代碼</option>
									<option value="school">學校名稱</option>
									<option value="dept">系所名稱</option>
									<option value="mainGroup">學群</option>
								</select>
							</div>
							<div class="col-7">
								<div class="input-group">
									<input type="text" id="input-optionFilter" class="form-control" id="" placeholder="關鍵字">
									<span class="input-group-btn">
										<button id="btn-manualSearch" class="btn btn-secondary" type="button">
											<i class="fa fa-search" aria-hidden="true"></i>
										</button>
									</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<hr>

						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-12">
								<table class="table table-hover">
									<tbody id="optionalWish-list">
									</tbody>
								</table>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-12">
								<table class="table table-hover">
									<div id="pagination-container"></div>
								</table>
							</div>
						</div>

					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xl-6">
				<div class="card card-bottom">
					<div class="card-header">已填選志願</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<table class="table table-hover">
							<tbody id="wish-list">
							</tbody>
						</table>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="row">
	<div class="col-md text-center">
		<button id="btn-save" class="btn btn-primary" role="button">儲存</button>
	</div>
</div>

